Package net.ssehub.comani.analysis.deadcodechange.diff

Class AnalysisResult

java.lang.Object
net.ssehub.comani.analysis.deadcodechange.diff.AnalysisResult
public class AnalysisResult
extends java.lang.Object
This class represent the results of the analysis of a particular commit as provided by the DiffAnalyzer.
Author:
Christian Kroeher
